## From connected to Intelligent

- · Autonomous supply chain through best-in-class data governance model and architecture, extract full value leveraging intelligent automation and advanced data analytics, and leverage our digital incubator for innovation (e.g., AI, 5G);
- · Smart operations powered by EcoStruxure ™ , connecting all smart sites, deploy flexible automation, self-optimization of processes and assets through a library of analytics, and deploy smart centers of excellence;
